AC_LIBTOOL_DLOPEN
AM_PROG_LIBTOOL


dnl Header-file checks
AC_HEADER_STDC

dnl Checks for the optional plugins
dnl ===========================================================================

AC_SUBST(OPTIONAL_PLUGINS)
